Hey, say hello to the piglins of 1.14! I think you know who they are.

If not, then listen up. Piglins are very similar to zombie pigmen, but they will be aggressive towards you if you don't have gold armor on you (that is, they will be aggressive towards you ALWAYS, because I don't know how you'll survive in hell wearing gold armor). Also, if you throw them a gold bar, they'll be willing to trade it for something else.
